channel.title: [317 - DELTA] OleanPkz - Web Client, great server, NEED GFX DESIGNER [read]
channel.description:
OleanPkz is my server that I have been working on for quite some time now. I plan on putting it online February 20th hosted on a VPS. On the 17th I will begin to make a web client. (Well, try anyways.) Following the Web Client I will apply for a position on MoparScape's Server Status Page for a sponsored spot on the Top 8.
Right now everything looks great, but I need someone to make good looking interface's.
I need it to look nice and I can't make stuff look nice with paint.
If you could help, I'm sure we could arrange some sort of "donation".
